	<h1>Keyboard Shortcuts</h1>
	<table>
	  <tr class='odd'>
	    <th class='title'>Close Program</th>
	    <th class='key'>Windows: Ctrl+Q<br />OS X: cmd+Q</th>
	    <th class='disc'>Stops the program from running, closing out of any dialog windows it controls, and removes the toolbar icon.</th>
	  </tr>
	  <tr >
	    <th class='title'>Add Table Entry</th>
	    <th class='key'>Windows: Ctrl+Shift+A<br />OS X: cmd+Shift+A</th>
	    <th class='disc'>Adds a new table row to the currently being viewed table. This also saves the currently viewed table after adding the tab.</th>
	  </tr>
	  <tr class='odd'>
	    <th class='title'>Remove Table Entry</th>
	    <th class='key'>Windows: Ctrl+Del<br />OS X: cmd+Del</th>
	    <th class='disc'>Removes a new table row to the currently being viewed table. This also saves the currently viewed table after removeing the tab.</th>
	  </tr>
	  </tr>
	  <tr >
	    <th class='title'>Find Entry</th>
	    <th class='key'>Windows: Ctrl+F<br />OS X: cmd+F</th>
	    <th class='disc'>Goes to the next item containing the text from the search box.</th>
	  </tr>
	  <tr class='odd'>
	    <th class='title'>Save Current Tab</th>
	    <th class='key'>Windows: Ctrl+S<br />OS X: cmd+S</th>
	    <th class='disc'>Saves the work done in the current tab to it's database file.</th>
	  </tr>
	</table>
</body>
